    title: "Webflow Education Templates: Courses and Learning Platforms",
    excerpt: "Create education and course platform templates with lesson management, progress tracking, and enrollment flows.",
    content: "<p>Online education is a booming market, and educators need professional websites to sell courses, manage students, and deliver content. Webflow templates for education fill this gap with beautiful design and functional CMS architecture.</p><h2>Course Catalog Design</h2><p>Build a course catalog using Webflow CMS with fields for: course title, instructor, duration, difficulty level, price, curriculum outline, video preview, and student count. Design the catalog with grid and list view options, filtering by category, and sorting by popularity or date.</p><h2>Lesson Structure</h2><p>Design a lesson page template with: video player embed, lesson description, downloadable resources, next/previous navigation, and progress indicator. Use Webflow's CMS relationships to connect courses, modules, and individual lessons in a hierarchical structure.</p><h2>Enrollment and Payment</h2><p>Include a clean enrollment flow: course preview, pricing options (one-time or subscription), checkout form, and confirmation page. For membership-based learning platforms, integrate with Webflow Memberships to gate course content by subscription tier.</p><p>Education templates are a growing category on Flowbites. Course creators and universities are investing in online presence, and templates that understand the education workflow — from enrollment to completion — command premium prices.</p>",
